{"tid":1470431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林日曦：有冇留意，一直以來親建制都係極團結的。","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:48:02.000Z","uid":270196,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c4c3df75e519ff1ed7b369aeaba975110b49dd","tid":1470431,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2409079429184048?s=1067075361&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2409079429184048%3Fs%3D1067075361%26sfns%3Dmo&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w8pe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=a7033e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2409079429184048?s=1067075361&amp;sfns=mo</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">有冇留意，一直以來親建制都係極團結的。</span><br />\n你先唔好理佢哋嘅團結係唔係為咗利益，<br />\n係唔係冇自由意志，<br />\n總之佢哋就係好團結。<br />\n甚至乎佢哋嘅成功，就係源於團結。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你見佢哋其實係甚少會公開批評同路建制仔。<br />\n(有時都會嘅，但比起嚟真係好少)</span><br />\n好似何姓元朗大總統啲行為咁癲，<br />\n好多親建制中產或者親建制評論人，<br />\n暗地裏可能都唔認同阿總統，<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但佢哋冇公開叫佢應該點、唔應該點，最多私下教路。<br />\n佢哋最能體現到咩叫不指責不篤灰不割蓆。</span>"},{"pid":"81820c4cd18b096212dda78f13553b07d593cbc6","tid":1470431,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d341f589e7b0dd72ff6c40f79f4964204fd1188","tid":1470431,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"喺連登苦口婆心教路<br />\n<br />\n係有部份人堅持做緊的"},{"pid":"7ca2a81bb2d13d0d11d11b2978ad8dbb3ee01cd8","tid":1470431,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc946495213148322ec1bb06eaf6cc13cf3dd72c","tid":1470431,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0fba11bdd96d72705e2ea0b4ec60e8d7bdb856","tid":1470431,"uid":276758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"呢樣真,要推<br />\n學到對家一半,就已經冇得輸<br />\n我地有大量黑材料係手,反而成日自亂陣腳,有事就9秒9出po屌,割蓆,打沉大家既意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家係差在睇埋我地幾時內訌,咁成場運動正式收皮。"},{"pid":"688dc945fce2ab89f30c6b28cef41ad30c15df5e","tid":1470431,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d341f589e7b0dd72ff6c40f79f4964204fd1188","tid":1470431,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"喺連登苦口婆心教路<br />\n<br />\n係有部份人堅持做緊的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"要自己人多過五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616064d08f27dd3c794a54be4bdca831235969b0","tid":1470431,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> push"}]}